id.description: The unique identifier of the API key

role.description: The user role assigned to the API key

name.description: The unique name of the API key

status.description:
The status of an API key.
Available values:
* `enabled`
* `disabled`

If-Match.description: The ETag of the resource you want to update. Note: The resource is updated only if the provided value matches the ETag of the resource.
